{"tid":1592365,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"政府催生「獅鳥」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-24T14:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T14:40:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e2139874db9581f29bdda5bcc08964c296318e31","tid":1592365,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190924/20773671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F20773671&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUv2u4%2BaHFFj7NdFJeB1nj9U%3D&h=84edbc87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F20773671&h=9524fa0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190924/20773671</a><br />\n<br />\n政府催生「獅鳥」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190924/large/1569227365_e96c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190924%2Flarge%2F1569227365_e96c.jpg&h=e821c4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使最平和怕事和理非，看到近日多宗元朗白衣黑幫被「獅鳥」事件，都大快人心。有人道：「這幾個月的鬱悶一掃而空！」<br />\n<br />\n──如何「一掃而空」？傷口太深，流血過多，山埃催淚煙令人人呼吸困難&hellip;&hellip;還有輕生、被黑警打死、被自殺、被毀屍滅跡的多條人命，還沒數得清，怎麼「空」？你們說治癒，「癒」遠遠未達，「治療」而已，血債血償天經地義。<br />\n<br />\n新神獸「獅鳥」的出現有因果，官逼民反，黑逼私了──鷹頭獅身的怪鳥，反映香港民防自衛新一章。「我哋唔係好恰㗎！」那把悽厲洩憤的女聲，就是「人若犯我我必還拖」的潛在能量，全靠林鄭政府警黑勾結姑息養奸所催生。<br />\n<br />\n黑幫賊匪頭破血流不支倒地了，他們一直橫行無差別恐襲，市民慘烈哀號全無還手之力。而本來除暴安良救急扶危男子漢，淪為欺善怕惡鋤弱扶強的黑警，不敢與勇武抗爭者正面衝突，只靠卧底夾擊，還賤格得專門恰細路（10歲都拉）、侵少女、攻擊記者、救護員、走避不及的老弱&hellip;&hellip;「獅鳥」應運而生替天行道，那些政棍人渣賣港賊也驚到鼻哥窿冇肉。<br />\n<br />\n其實無人希望獅鳥演變成死亡之鳥，但何以智商奇低，心腸歹毒之掌權者，樂看廝殺？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n有膽就跟連登仔對話 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n哀悼大牙（上） (鄧達智)"},{"pid":"08a4ff7ebbf9083f1bb38b08982c5b75b6b96fd7","tid":1592365,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"［請幫推行動post］今星期四：和你塞 美心MX<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4KHbAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4KHbAX.jpg&h=3211b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fdfd3c25b2ef3c333520cbf0eb404dc167bbc41","tid":1592365,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"baf78fc8aae81a43bf93320f39c0aa27a45f258a","tid":1592365,"uid":263680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"[下一步升級行動] 點解唔可以有第二次佔中?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592335</a>"}]}